                                Accommodation                                                                                                                  Dublin   Students at our Dublin campuses can take advantage of Griffith Halls of Residence, conveniently located on-campus. It houses over 600 students and is within walking distance of Dublin city centre on the South Circular Road.          Students may also opt to find private accommodation.                                                                                                                                                                                                                          Cork   There are numerous student accommodation sites throughout the city.   Options include:     Deanshall      EazyCity     Hatch     Nido Student     VivaIreland     Stay Cork    Host families are also available - enquire with the admissions office for more information.     The admissions office will be happy to offer guidance on the transit options available to reach the campus.                                                                                                                                                                                                                          Limerick   There are numerous student accommodation sites throughout the city.   Options include:     Thomond Village     Brookfield Hall     City Campus     The admissions office will be happy to offer guidance on the transit options available to reach the campus.                                                                                                                                                         